---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body class="h-full flex flex-col gap-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
    <Header />
    <main class="h-full px-8 flex flex-col gap-4 mt-4 md:mt-14">
      <h1>Hello World!</h1>
      <p>
        I'm Fahri, a software developer specializing in mobile and web
        development with over <strong>six years of experience</strong>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Currently, I work as a fullstack developer at <a
          class="link"
          href="https://ebuddy.gg"
          target="_blank">ebuddy.gg</a
        >, a social app focused on companionship where people can connect, share
        experiences, and build meaningful relationships.
      </p>
      <p>
        Previously, I developed education platforms at Telkom Indonesia until
        March 2025, including Pijar Mahir and Pijar Sekolah.
      </p>
      <p>
        I work with various web and mobile technologies including
        <strong>React</strong>, <strong>Next.js</strong>, <strong
          >React Native</strong
        >, <strong>Jetpack Compose</strong>, and <strong>SwiftUI</strong>.
        Ultimately, these are just tools for solving problems and bringing ideas
        to life.
      </p>
      <p>
        I love building experiences that look great and feel even better to use.
        Check out some of my work, including interactive animation experiments,
        on <a
          href="https://github.com/fahrimz/oneDayOneSlice/tree/main/results/README.md"
          target="_blank"
          class="link">GitHub</a
        >.
      </p>
      <p>
        Beyond code, I love exploring web novels, games and moviesâ€”sources of
        creativity that often spark new ideas. If you're into tech, creative
        challenges, or just want to chat about these, let's connect!
      </p>
      <p>You can find me here:</p>
      <ul class="flex gap-4">
        <li>
          <a class="link" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/fahrimz"
            >GitHub</a
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <a class="link" target="_blank" href="https://linkedin.com/in/fahrimz"
            >Linkedin</a
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
